name: Kewl Club x Morphs Snow Problem: Mini Comic

metadata.name: Kewl Club x Morphs 'Snow Problem: Mini Comic
metadata.description: Kewl Club has collaborated with Morphs, an upcoming artist with a versatile & ever-evolving art-style that can best be described as nerdy with a tinge of adorable. Morphs' work offers a more wholesome and fun take on things. Bringing together Morphs' affinity for comic books and Christmas, Kewl Club is proud to present 'Snow Problem. This drop is available to all Kewl Club members and Unstoppable Domains holders on Ethereum. Download the entire comic: https://mgate.io/go/hJGF1kjJZwCj
